snippet.title: Robopon 2 Cross Version Speedrun - 4:48:35 (Emulator)
snippet.description: Note: This run was not livestreamed, and was done with the VBA-M emulator, which is not a legitimate emulator for speedrunning GBA games (Runs slightly faster than normal, I believe), so this run is not valid.
